T O D O
-------

Must-haves in order to release
------------------------------
* Full configuration via PostgreSQL GUC settings as well db API

* Full support for the Redis API
	+ Support for Redis 1.2+ aswell as 2+

* Documentation

* Support for mset/mget



Nice-to-haves
-------------
* Sharding and support for multiple Redis servers

* Offline caching to be applied when Redis comes back online?

* Redis server reconnection (separate worker thread with keepalive/reconnections?)

